"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"8fcd66",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Work-related asthma (occupation-related asthma)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"7edc04",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Key is to diagnose airways disease in conjunction with exposure. Preshift and postshift spirometry, serial peak flow measurements, methacholine challenge test, inhalational challenge test; serologic tests for specific antigens."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-1 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"ac2065",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Occupational COPD"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"029039",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Pulmonary function tests showing obstruction; may develop in nonsmokers also."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-2 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"4b98fe",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Diffuse parenchymal lung diseases"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"c52b47",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"High-resolution CT is the imaging modality of choice. Pulmonary function tests show mixed restrictive and obstructive physiology."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-3 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"581349",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Dust-related pneumoconiosis"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"d41d8c",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[

]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-3 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"106c05",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Silica (acute silicosis, chronic simple silicosis, chronic complicated silicosis, accelerated silicosis)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"fedb3d",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Silica exposure in industries that cut or grind silica-containing materials, sandblasting, hydraulic fracking for natural gas. Silica exposure associated with increased risk for tuberculosis and autoimmune diseases. Imaging shows ground-glass, nodular, interstitial, or fibrotic infiltrates."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-3 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"d0e08b",
"class":"cell txt li",
"children":[
"Coal (simple or complicated coal-worker's pneumoconiosis)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"46d06e",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Less common today given improved mine safety standards. Imaging shows nodular or fibrotic changes."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-4 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"9dd726",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Asbestos-related pleuropulmonary disease"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"5327c4",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Long latency (>25 years) from exposure to onset. Amphibole asbestos more pathogenic than serpentine asbestos. Pulmonary fibrosis and pleural disease (effusions, plaques, pleural thickening)."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-5 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"e06b88",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Metal-induced lung disease"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"857aa8",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Cobalt: giant cell interstitial pneumonitis. Indium: pulmonary alveolar proteinosis. Imaging shows ground-glass opacities."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-6 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"9d20e5",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Occupational hypersensitivity pneumonitis"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"59eb0e",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Typically acute or subacute in the occupational setting."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-7 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"471595",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Chronic beryllium disease (CBD)"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"549cb8",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Beryllium use in aerospace, automotive, nuclear, and telecommunication industries. Exposure in a patient with a granulomatous lung disease should prompt consideration of CBD. Diagnosed by beryllium lymphocyte proliferation test."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-8 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"2374d7",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Lung malignancies"
]
},
" "
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"506e2f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Lung cancer (histologic subtypes vary with type of exposure), mesothelioma (strongly associated with asbestos exposure)."
]
},
" "
]
}
]
}
]
}
]
},
